   <div class="teaser_fmt"> 
    <h3>Acne Overview</h3> 
    <p>Acne may be treated with a combination of remedies including over-the-counter skin care, acne medications, and chemical or laser procedures. Learn safe ways to banish blackheads, whiteheads, and cystic acne, and get the clear skin you want. </p> 
