    <h3>Skin Conditions and Acne</h3>
    <div class="snippet_fmt" id="art-snp">
     <p xmlns:xalan="http://xml.apache.org/xalan">Most people develop acne-- the most common skin condition -- to some degree, but it primarily affects teenagers undergoing hormonal changes.</p>
     <p xmlns:xalan="http://xml.apache.org/xalan">Acne may be mild (few, occasional pimples), moderate (inflammatory papules), or severe (nodules and cysts). Treatment depends on the severity of the condition.</p>
    </div>
